attr
Attribute: an attribute of a pet
     1. Change according to time.
     2. Change according to action.
     3. The effect of one attribute on other attributes, e.g., the age effect on height.


def
Action: Manipulate on one/serveral attributes; mapping to a button on the GUI.


item
Item: an item is a thing contains one/several attributes, e.g., a sausage contains "health" etc, plant contains "oxygen".
      If a pet get this item, then update the attributes of the pet.


string

int

float
